Ecole Notre Dame de la Providence de Karubanda ni ishuri ry'isumbuye ryibanda byumwihariko ku burezi bw'umwana w'umukobwa.

== '''Amateka''' ==
Iri shuri ryatangiye mu mwaka w'1957, rishinzwe n'ababikira basabira  roho zo muri pirigatori (Les soiers auxilliatrices plus les âmes du purugatoire). Mu gutangira kwaryo,ryari rije kwita ku burezi bw'umwana w'umukobwa, rikaba ryari riherereyebahazwi ubu nk'akarere ka Gisagara. Abana babakobwa baturukuga mu [[Rwanda]] n' i [[Burundi]] ariho baje kwiga bitewe nuko muri icyo gihe uburezi bw'umunwana w'umukobwa ntabwo bwari bufite agaciro. Ku bijyanye nibyahigirwaga rero,habaga  amasomo yibijyanye n'indimi, imirimo y'intoki,ubuzima bwo mu mutwe(psychology),ndetse nimyafatire y'abantu  (sociology)<ref name=":0">https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/10104</ref>.  

Mu mwaka w'1999,nibwo iri shuri ryahinduye izina,aho ryitwaga Ecole Sociale, rigahinduka Ecole Notre Dames de la providence de Karubanda. 

== '''Aho riherereye''' ==
Ecole Notre Dame de la Providence de Karubanda iherereye mu ntara y'amajyepho, [[Akarere ka Huye]],umurenge wa Ngoma, kuri metero 100 uvuye kuri garre nkuru ya [[Huye (Akarere)|Huye]].<ref>{{Cite web |title=Archive copy |url=http://www.endpk.org/ |accessdate=2021-01-24 |archive-date=2021-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130091759/http://www.endpk.org/ |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

